title: Hour 1 - Hugs Not Sacks, Eli Manning
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Hugs Not Sacks, Eli Manning
description:
Dan thinks the prevalence of roughing the passer calls is an overreaction. And Former NFL QB Eli Manning drops by to address what it's like being chased by 300lb defensive linemen.
